ary de 2022</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p><span style="color: #000000;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 14.6667px">Por el cual se convoca a sesiones extraordinarias al Concejo de Bucaramanga.</span></p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-123406"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/123406/DECRETO-0009-ENCARGO-ANA-LEONOR-RUEDA-VIVAS.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DECRETO-0009-ENCARGO-ANA-LEONOR-RUEDA-VIVAS.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/123406/DECRETO-0009-ENCARGO-ANA-LEONOR-RUEDA-VIVAS.pdf" target="_blank">Decreto 0009 de 2022</a><span class="shared-file-date">24 de January de 2022</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p><span style="color: #000000;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 14.6667px">Por el cual se hace un encargo</span></p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-123033"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/123033/RESOLUCION-0031-AMPLIA-INSCRIPCIONS-COMISION-EMPLEADOS.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/RESOLUCION-0031-AMPLIA-INSCRIPCIONS-COMISION-EMPLEADOS.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/123033/RESOLUCION-0031-AMPLIA-INSCRIPCIONS-COMISION-EMPLEADOS.pdf" target="_blank">Resolución 0031 de 2022</a><span class="shared-file-date">18 de January de 2022</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p><span style="color: #000000;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 14.6667px">Por la cual se amplía el período de inscripciones para candidatos a elección de representantes de los empleados ante la Comisión de Personal</span></p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-123043"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/123043/DECRETO-0007-HOMENAJE-POSTUMO-JOSE-CAVANZO-GUIZA.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DECRETO-0007-HOMENAJE-POSTUMO-JOSE-CAVANZO-GUIZA.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/123043/DECRETO-0007-HOMENAJE-POSTUMO-JOSE-CAVANZO-GUIZA.pdf" target="_blank">Decreto 0007 de 2022</a><span class="shared-file-date">17 de January de 2022</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p><span style="color: #000000;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 14.6667px">Por medio del cual se rinde homenaje póstumo al reconocido empresario santandereano JOSE CAVANZO GUIZAl</span></p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-122903"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/122903/DECRETO-0006-CONVOCA-INSTALCION-CONSEJO-MUNICIPAL-DE-JUVENTUD.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DECRETO-0006-CONVOCA-INSTALCION-CONSEJO-MUNICIPAL-DE-JUVENTUD.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/122903/DECRETO-0006-CONVOCA-INSTALCION-CONSEJO-MUNICIPAL-DE-JUVENTUD.pdf" target="_blank">Decreto 0006 de 2022</a><span class="shared-file-date">14 de January de 2022</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p><span style="color: #000000;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 14.6667px">Por medio del cual se convoca a la instalación del Consejo Municipal de Juventud de Bucaramanga y se dictan otras disposiciones</span></p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-122823"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/122823/DECRETO-0005-ACTUALIZACION-PGIRS.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/DECRETO-0005-ACTUALIZACION-PGIRS.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/122823/DECRETO-0005-ACTUALIZACION-PGIRS.pdf" target="_blank">Decreto 0005 de 2022</a><span class="shared-file-date">13 de January de 2022</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p><span style="color: #000000;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 14.6667px">POR EL CUAL SE ADOPTA LA ACTUALIZACIÓN DEL PLAN DE GESTIÓN INTEGRAL DE RESIDUOS SÓLIDOS -PGIRS- DEL MUNICIPIO DE BUCARAMANGA, Y SE DICTAN OTRAS DISPOSICIONES</span></p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-122822"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/122822/RESOLUCION-0004-PERMISO-REMUNERADO-Y-ENCARGO.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/RESOLUCION-0004-PERMISO-REMUNERADO-Y-ENCARGO.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/122822/RESOLUCION-0004-PERMISO-REMUNERADO-Y-ENCARGO.pdf" target="_blank">Resolución 0004 de 2022</a><span class="shared-file-date">12 de January de 2022</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p><span style="color: #000000;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 14.6667px">Por la cual se concede un permiso remunerado, un compensatorio y se realiza un encargo</span></p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-122774"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/122774/DECRETO-0004-INCORPORACION-RECURSOS-PRESUPUESTO-GENERAL-DE-RENTAS-Y-GASTOS.pdf"  data-external-url="https:/