tions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-90356"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/90356/0214-12062017.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0214-12062017.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/90356/0214-12062017.pdf" target="_blank">0214-12062017</a><span class="shared-file-date">14 de June de 2017</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0214 de 2017. Por la cual se actualiza la metodología de política de administración del riesgo para la administración municipal el alcalde municipal de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-90354"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/90354/0080-14062017.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0080-14062017.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/90354/0080-14062017.pdf" target="_blank">0080 14062017</a><span class="shared-file-date">14 de June de 2017</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0080 de 2017. Por el cual se modifica la composición del consejo de participación ciuda