d-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0195 de 2016. Por medio del cual se liquida el decreto 0191 de 2016. Presupuesto general de rentas gastos del 01 de enero al 31 de diciembre de 2017</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-90738"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/90738/0196-30122016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0196-30122016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/90738/0196-30122016.pdf" target="_blank">0196-30122016</a><span class="shared-file-date">31 de December de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0196 de 2016. Por el cual se efectúa una modificación al presupuesto de gastos vigencia 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-90736"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/90736/0197-30122016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0197-30122016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/90736/0197-30122016.pdf" target="_blank">0197-30122016</a><span class="shared-file-date">31 de December de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0197 de 2016. Por el cual se adopta la actualización del plan de gestión integral de residuos sólidos. PGIRS.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-90734"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/90734/0198-30122016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0198-30122016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/90734/0198-30122016.pdf" target="_blank">0198-30122016</a><span class="shared-file-date">31 de December de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0198 de 2016. Por el cual se incrementan las tarifas de los parqueaderos públicos de las categorías B,C y D del municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-90746"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/90746/0187-14122016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0187-14122016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/90746/0187-14122016.pdf" target="_blank">0187-14122016</