 class="shared-files-card-91491"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91491/0013-10022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0013-10022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91491/0013-10022016.pdf" target="_blank">0013-10022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Por medio de la cual se delega la responsabilidad de rendir la cuenta que corresponda a cada módulo para el Software del SIA OBSERVA de la Contraloría Municipal.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91489"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91489/0014-17022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0014-17022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91489/0014-17022016.pdf" target="_blank">0014-17022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0014 De 2016, Por medio de la cual se Por el cual se hace un encargo, a la Dra Melba Fabiola Clavijo.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91487"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91487/0090-18022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0090-18022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91487/0090-18022016.pdf" target="_blank">0090-18022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0090 de 2016. Por la cual se adopta la escala de viáticos establecidos en el decreto 231 de febrero de 2016, expedida por el gobierno nacional.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91485"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91485/0182-18022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0182-18022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91485/0182-18022016.pdf" target="_blank">0182-18022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0182 de 2016, Por medio de la cual se modifica temporalmente el horario de trabajo en la administración municipal.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91483"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91483/0015-19022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0015-19022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91483/0015-19022016.pdf" target="_blank">0015-19022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0015 de 2016, Por el cual deroga el decreto 0002 de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91481"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91481/0016-24022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0016-24022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91481/0016-24022016.pdf" target="_blank">0016-24022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto N 0016 de 2016. Por la cual se efectúan una modificación al anexo del decreto de liquidación del presupuesto de gastos del municipio de Bucaramanga vigencia 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91479"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91479/0018-26022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0018-26022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91479/0018-26022016.pdf" target="_blank">0018-26022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0018 de 2016, Por medio del cual se nombran los miembros del consejo territorial de planeación del municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91477"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91477/0019-29022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0019-29022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91477/0019-29022016.pdf" target="_blank">0019-29022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0019 de 2016, por medio de la cual se por el cual se hace un encargo, a la Dra. Melba Fabiola Clavijo.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91475"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91475/0201-29022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0201-29022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91475/0201-29022016.pdf" target="_blank">0201-29022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Por medio del cual se modifica parcialmente el artículo 3° de 16. Resolución 1625 de 16 de diciembre de 2015.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91473"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91473/0020-03032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0020-03032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91473/0020-03032016.pdf" target="_blank">0020-03032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0020 de 2016, por el cual se unifica, fija y distribuye la planta de empleos del municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91471"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91471/0021-03032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0021-03032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91471/0021-03032016.pdf" target="_blank">0021-03032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0021 de 2016, Por el cual se modifica el Decreto 232 de diciembre de 2015 y se ajusta el Manual específico de Funciones y Competencias Laborales para algunos empleos de la Planta de Personal del Municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91469"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91469/0023-09032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0023-09032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91469/0023-09032016.pdf" target="_blank">0023-09032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0023 de 2016, por medio del cual se regula la política de privacidad y manejo de la información de las hojas de vida recepcionadas para conformar la base de datos de personas interesadas en acceder a contratar servicios profesionales y de apoyo a la gestión con el Municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91464"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91464/0024-16032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0024-16032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91464/0024-16032016.pdf" target="_blank">0024-16032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0024 de 2016, Por el cual se realizan unos ajustes al presupuesto general de rentas y gastos del municipio vigencia 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91460"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91460/0025-16032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0025-16032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91460/0025-16032016.pdf" target="_blank">0025-16032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0025 de 2016, Por el cual se adoptan medidas con el fin de conservar el orden público durante el paro nacional programado para el 17 de marzo de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91456"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91456/0213-18032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0213-18032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91456/0213-18032016.pdf" target="_blank">0213-18032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0213 de 2016. Por medio del cual se declaran administrativamente como hábiles los días 19, 22 y 23 de marzo de 2016 para efectos administrativos contractuales.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91453"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91453/0017-26022016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0017-26022016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91453/0017-26022016.pdf" target="_blank">0017-26022016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto N 0017 de 2016. Por la cual se efectúan una modificación al anexo del decreto de liquidación del presupuesto de gastos del municipio de Bucaramanga vigencia 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91450"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91450/0028-30032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0028-30032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91450/0028-30032016.pdf" target="_blank">0028-30032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Por el cual se hace un encargo.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91445"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91445/0029-30032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0029-30032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91445/0029-30032016.pdf" target="_blank">0029-30032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Por el cual se crea el comité antitramites y de gobierno en línea Del municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91442"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91442/0228-30032016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0228-30032016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91442/0228-30032016.pdf" target="_blank">0228-30032016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Por medio del cual se aclara la Resolución 0134 del 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91440"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91440/0031-05042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0031-05042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91440/0031-05042016.pdf" target="_blank">0031-05042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">DECRETO 0031 DE 2016. Por medio de la cual se hace un encargo, a la Dra. OLGA PATRICIA CHACÓN ARIAS.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91438"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91438/0033-08042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0033-08042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91438/0033-08042016.pdf" target="_blank">0033-08042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0033 de 2016. Por medio del cual se modifica el decreto no. 004 del 20 de enero de 2016, “Por el cual se delega la Contratación Administrativa en los Servidores Públicos del nivel directivo de la Administración Municipal.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91436"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91436/0034-08042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0034-08042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91436/0034-08042016.pdf" target="_blank">0034-08042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0034 de 2016. Por la cual se crea el comité de seguimiento operativo municipal al programa de alimentación escolar PAE.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91434"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91434/0035-08042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0035-08042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91434/0035-08042016.pdf" target="_blank">0035-08042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0035 de 2016. Por medio de la cual se delega al director del departamento administrativo de la defensoría del espacio público la celebración de contratos para desarrollar los programas de recuperación y preservación del espacio público en el municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91432"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91432/0036-11042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0036-11042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91432/0036-11042016.pdf" target="_blank">0036-11042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0036 de 2016. Por medio de la cual se hace un encargo, al DR. IGNACIO PEREZ CADENA.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91430"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91430/0037-14042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0037-14042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91430/0037-14042016.pdf" target="_blank">0037-14042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0037 de 2016. Por el cual se designa una comisión para el estudio de pliego de peticiones presentado por sindicatos del sector educativo.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91428"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91428/0039-18042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0039-18042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91428/0039-18042016.pdf" target="_blank">0039-18042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0039 de 2016. Por el cual se determina el incremento salarial para los funcionarios de la alcaldía central municipal vigencia 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91423"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91423/0254-18042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0254-18042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91423/0254-18042016.pdf" target="_blank">0254-18042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0254 de 2016. Por la cual se fija la tabla de valores de auxilios económicos a asignar, como ayuda humanitaria inmediata a personas víctimas del conflicto armado.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91420"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91420/0040-21042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0040-21042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91420/0040-21042016.pdf" target="_blank">0040-21042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0040 de 2016. Por el cual se adoptan medidas con el fin de conservar el orden público durante los comicios para elegir los representantes de las juntas de acción comunal para el 24 de abril de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91413"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91413/0042-21042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0042-21042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91413/0042-21042016.pdf" target="_blank">0042-21042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0042 de 2016. Por el cual se cita al honorable concejo municipal a sesiones extraordinarias.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91408"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91408/0257-21042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0257-21042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91408/0257-21042016.pdf" target="_blank">0257-21042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0257 de 2016. Por la cual se declara administrativamente como día hábil el día 24 de abril de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91406"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91406/0042-22042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0042-22042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91406/0042-22042016.pdf" target="_blank">0042-22042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0042 de 2016. Por el cual se modifica el decreto 0042 del 21 de abril de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91404"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91404/0044-22042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0044-22042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91404/0044-22042016.pdf" target="_blank">0044-22042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0044 de 2016. Por el cual se corrige un error formal dentro del decreto 0042 del 22 de abril del 2016</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91402"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91402/0046-22042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0046-22042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91402/0046-22042016.pdf" target="_blank">0046-22042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0046 de 2016. Por el cual se hace un encargo.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91401"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91401/0047-22042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/0047-22042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91401/0047-22042016.pdf" target="_blank">0047-22042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0047 de 2016. Por medio del cual se modifica el decreto 0040 de 2016 por el cual “se adoptan medidas con el fin de conservar el orden público en el municipio de Bucaramanga el próximo 24 de abril, establecido como día de los comicios para elegir los representantes de las juntas de acción comunal”.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91399"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91399/0043-22042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0043-22042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91399/0043-22042016.pdf" target="_blank">0043-22042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0043 de 2016. Por el cual se modifica el decreto No. 0042 del 21 de abril del 2016</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91397"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91397/0048-27042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0048-27042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91397/0048-27042016.pdf" target="_blank">0048-27042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0048 de 2016. Por el cual se rinde homenaje y reconocimiento póstumo exaltando la memoria del caricaturista maestro MATIAS ERI BLANCO PINEDA.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91395"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91395/0050-27042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0050-27042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91395/0050-27042016.pdf" target="_blank">0050-27042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0050 de 2016. Por el cual se adoptan medidas de policía, necesarias para garantizar la seguridad ciudadana, la protección de los menores, las libertades públicas.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91393"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91393/0052-28042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0052-28042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91393/0052-28042016.pdf" target="_blank">0052-28042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0052 de 2016. Por el cual se adiciona el periodo de sesiones extraordinarias del concejo municipal convocadas mediante el decreto 0042, y se incorpora un proyecto de acuerdo.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91391"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91391/0266-28042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0266-28042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91391/0266-28042016.pdf" target="_blank">0266-28042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0266 de 2016. por la cual se designa el funcionario líder para el desarrollo de las estrategias del comité antitramites y de gobierno en línea, eficiencia administrativa y política cero papel en el municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91387"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91387/0268-29042016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0268-29042016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91387/0268-29042016.pdf" target="_blank">0268-29042016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0268 de 2016. Por medio de la cual se declara como horas hábiles el día 29 de abril de 2016 desde la 1:15 pm hasta las 08:00 pm para efectos administrativos contractuales.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91385"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91385/0055-02052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0055-02052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91385/0055-02052016.pdf" target="_blank">0055-02052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">DECRETO 0055 DE 2016 POR EL CUAL SE RECLASIFICAN UNOS EMPLEOS, SE SUPRIMEN UNOS CARGOS DE TRABAJADORES OFICIALES Y SE CREAN UNOS CARGOS DE EMPLEADOS PUBLICOS EN LA PLANTA DE PERSONAL DEL MUNICIPIO DE BUCARAMANGA</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91381"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91381/0056-02052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0056-02052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91381/0056-02052016.pdf" target="_blank">0056-02052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0056 de 2016. Por el cual se adiciona el Decreto 232 de diciembre de 2015 y 021 de 3 de marzo de 2016 y se asignan funciones y competencias laborales de la Planta de Personal del Municipio de Bucaramanga</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91377"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91377/0270-03052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0270-03052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91377/0270-03052016.pdf" target="_blank">0270-03052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">RESOLUCION 0270 DE 2016 POR LA CUAL SE EFECTUAN UNAS INCORPORACIONES A CARGOS DE EMPLEADOS PUBLICOS EN LA PLANTA DE PERSONAL DEL MUNICIPIO DE BUCARAMANGA</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91370"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91370/0059-06052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0059-06052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91370/0059-06052016.pdf" target="_blank">0059-06052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0059 DE 2016.Por el cual se hace un encargo.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91360"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91360/0062-18052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0062-18052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91360/0062-18052016.pdf" target="_blank">0062-18052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0062 de 2016. Por el cual se adiciona en pazo las sesiones extraordinarias del concejo municipal convocadas mediante el decreto 0042, y adicionadas en el decreto 0052 de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91358"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91358/0064-18052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0064-18052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91358/0064-18052016.pdf" target="_blank">0064-18052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0064 de 2016. Por medio del cual se establece la delegación para la formulación, y elaboración del plan de salud territorial 2016-2019, acorde con las políticas de plan decenal de salud pública 2012-2021.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91354"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91354/0281-23052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0281-23052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91354/0281-23052016.pdf" target="_blank">0281-23052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0281 de 2016. Por la cual se adopta plan de incentivos para los funcionarios de carrera administrativa y libre nombramiento y remoción.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91347"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91347/0282-24052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0282-24052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91347/0282-24052016.pdf" target="_blank">0282-24052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0282 de 2016.por la cual se reconocen unos auxilios económicos como ayuda humanitaria inmediata a personas víctimas del conflicto armado recibidas en el municipio de Bucaramanga, y se encuentran pendientes de inscripción en el registro único de víctimas, en cumplimiento de la ley 1448 de 2011.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91342"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91342/0066-25052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0066-25052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91342/0066-25052016.pdf" target="_blank">0066-25052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0066 de 2016. Por el cual se corrige decretos 0055 y 0056 del 02 de mayo de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91332"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91332/0068-26052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/0068-26052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91332/0068-26052016.pdf" target="_blank">0068-26052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0068 de 2016. Por medio del cual se crea y adopta el manual de actividades, labores y requisitos mínimos para los trabajadores oficiales .</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91321"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91321/0286-2605215.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0286-2605215.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91321/0286-2605215.pdf" target="_blank">0286-2605215</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0286 de 2016. Por la cual corrige la resolución 0270 de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91291"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91291/0069-27052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0069-27052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91291/0069-27052016.pdf" target="_blank">0069-27052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">DECRETO 0069 DE 2016. POR EL CUAL SE DEJA SIN EFECTO EL DECRETO 0067 DE 26 DE MAYO DE 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91289"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91289/0070-27052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0070-27052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91289/0070-27052016.pdf" target="_blank">0070-27052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0070 de 2016. Por el cual se adiciona en plazo las sesiones extraordinarias del concejo municipal convocadas mediante el decreto 0042, y adicionadas en el decreto 0052 de 2016, y decreto 0062.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91287"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91287/0071-31052016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0071-31052016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91287/0071-31052016.pdf" target="_blank">0071-31052016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0071 de 2016. Por el cual se hace un encargo a la DRA MELBA FABIOLA CLAVIJO DE JACOME.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91285"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91285/0074-03062016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0074-03062016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91285/0074-03062016.pdf" target="_blank">0074-03062016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Decreto 0074 de 2016. Por medio de la cual se adopta el acuerdo colectivo vigencia 2016, suscrito por la organización sindical SIPRECOL y el municipio de Bucaramanga.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91284"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91284/0321-17062016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/0321-17062016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91284/0321-17062016.pdf" target="_blank">0321-17062016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Por la cual se declara administrativamente como día hábil los días 19 y 26 de junio de 2016</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="share