nts"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91051/0409-19082016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0409-19082016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91051/0409-19082016.pdf" target="_blank">0409-19082016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de August de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0409 de 2016. Por la cual se modifica el horario de trabajo en la administración municipal.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-91270"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/91270/0391-01082016.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/0391-01082016.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/91270/0391-01082016.pdf" target="_blank">0391-01082016</a><span class="shared-file-date">25 de January de 2016</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">Resolución 0391 de 2016. Por la cual se modifica el artículo primero de la resolución nº 0254 de 2016.</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-88594"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/88594/DECRETO-0038-MODIFICA-MANUAL-DE-CONTRATACION.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/DECRETO-0038-MODIFICA-MANUAL-DE-CONTRATACION.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/88594/DECRETO-0038-MODIFICA-MANUAL-DE-CONTRATACION.pdf" target="_blank">DECRETO 0038 DEL 20 DE MARZO DE 2019</a><span class="shared-file-date">21 de March de 0219</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">POR MEDIO DEL CUAL SE MODIFICA EL MANUAL DE CONTRATACIÓN DEL MUNICIPIO DE BUCARAMANGA</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li><li class="shared-files-card-87296"><div class="shared-files-main-elements"><div class="shared-files-main-elements-left" style="background: url(https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/plugins/shared-files-pro/img/pdf.png) right top no-repeat; background-size: 48px;"></div><div class="shared-files-main-elements-right"><a class="shared-files-file-title"  data-file-type=""  data-file-url="/shared-files/87296/Decreto-0036-de-2021.pdf"  data-external-url="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Decreto-0036-de-2021.pdf"  data-image-url="" href="/shared-files/87296/Decreto-0036-de-2021.pdf" target="_blank">Decreto 0036 de 2021</a><span class="shared-file-date">6 de March de 0021</span><div class="shared-file-description-container"><p style="font-size: 10px">“POR MEDIO DEL CUAL SE DICTAN MEDIDAS DE ORDEN PÚBLICO DURANTE EL AISLAMIENTO SELECTIVO CON DISTANCIAMIENTO INDIVIDUAL RESPONSABLE, ORDENADO EN EL DECRETO NACIONAL No. 206 DEL 26 DE FEBRERO DE 2021 Y SE DICTAN OTRAS DISPOSICIONES EN VIRTUD DE LA EMERGENCIA SANITARIA GENERADA POR LA PANDEMIA DEL CORONAVIRUS COVID-19”</p></div><div class="shared-files-edit-actions"></div></div></div></li></ul><hr class="clear" /><div class="shared-files-pagination-improved"><div class="shared-files-pagination-improved-more-files">Browse files:</div><span aria-current="page" class="page-numbers current">1</span> <a class="page-numbers" href="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/transparencia-bucaramanga/sistema-de-busquedas-de-normas-propio-de-la-entidad/?_page=2&#038;_paged=default">2</a> <a class="page-numbers" href="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/transparencia-bucaramanga/sistema-de-busquedas-de-normas-propio-de-la-entidad/?_page=3&#038;_paged=default">3</a> <span class="page-numbers dots">&hellip;</span> <a class="page-numbers" href="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/transparencia-bucaramanga/sistema-de-busquedas-de-normas-propio-de-la-entidad/?_page=201&#038;_paged=default">201</a> <a class="next page-numbers" href="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/transparencia-bucaramanga/sistema-de-busquedas-de-normas-propio-de-la-entidad/?_page=2&#038;_paged=default">Siguiente &raquo;</a></div><div class="shared-files-nothing-found">No se han encontrado archivos.</div></div></div></div><hr class="clear" /></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_1 et_section_regular" ><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_1 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters4"><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_1  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_4 et_clickable  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h4>Decretos y Resoluciones antes del 2016</h4></div></div></div></div></div><ul class="kiwi-article-bar rect kiwi-article-bar-center " data-tracking="true" data-tracking-container="article-bar"><li><a data-class="popup" data-network="facebook" class="kiwi-nw-facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bucaramanga.gov.co%2Ftransparencia-bucaramanga%2Fsistema-de-busquedas-de-normas-propio-de-la-entidad%2F" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="kicon-facebook"></span> </a></li><li><a data-class="popup" data-network="twitter" class="kiwi-nw-twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Sistema%20de%20búsquedas%20de%20normas,%20propio%20de%20la%20entidad&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bucaramanga.gov.co%2Ftransparencia-bucaramanga%2Fsistema-de-busquedas-de-normas-propio-de-la-entidad%2F&#038;via=AlcaldiaBGA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="kicon-twitter"></span> </a></li><li><a data-class="popup" class="kiwi-nw-whatsapp" data-network="whatsapp" href="https://wa.me/?text=Look%20at%20this:%20Sistema+de+b%C3%BAsquedas+de+normas%2C+propio+de+la+entidad%20-%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bucaramanga.gov.co%2Ftransparencia-bucaramanga%2Fsistema-de-busquedas-de-normas-propio-de-la-entidad%2F" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="kicon-whatsapp"></span> </a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="et_post_meta_wrapper"><section id="comment-wrap"><h1 id="comments" class="page_title">1 Comentario</h1><ol class="commentlist clearfix"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1 et-pb-non-builder-comment" id="li-comment-4958"><article id="comment-4958" class="comment-body clearfix"><div class="comment_avatar"></div><div class="comment_postinfo"> <span class="fn">SERGIO RODRIGUEZ ROMERO</span> <span class="comment_date"> el 6 de febrero de 2025 a las 14:25 </span></div><div class="comment_area"><div class="comment-content clearfix"><p>Realizamos la creación de empresa bajo el código CIIU Actividad principal Código CIIU: 4773 En la ciudad de b/manga, requerimos saber cuales es el tramite para registrarnos en la alcandía de Bucaramanga para cumplir con las contribuciones de la ciudad. Requerimos nos ayuden con las tarifas y fechas las cuales se presentan los impuestos.</p></div></div></article></li><!-- #comment-## --></ol></section></div></article></div></div></div></div><footer class="et-l et-l--footer"><div class="et_builder_inner_content et_pb_gutters3"><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_0_tb_footer et_pb_with_background et_section_regular" ><div class="et_pb_with_border et_pb_row et_pb_row_0_tb_footer et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters2"><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_0_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_0_tb_footer  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h3 class="text-white">Alcaldía de Bucaramanga</h3><h5 class="font-weight-bold">Sede principal</h5></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_1_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_0_tb_footer"> <span class="et_pb_image_wrap "><noscript><img decoding="async" width="512" height="459" src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_512,h_459/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/escudo-alcaldia.png" alt="alcaldia-de-bga-logo" title="alcaldia-de-bga-logo" srcset="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_512/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/escudo-alcaldia.png 512w, https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_480/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/escudo-alcaldia-480x430.png 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 512px, 100vw" class="wp-image-209607" /></noscript><img decoding="async" width="512" height="459" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20512%20459%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_512,h_459/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/escudo-alcaldia.png" alt="alcaldia-de-bga-logo" title="alcaldia-de-bga-logo" data-srcset="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_512/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/escudo-alcaldia.png 512w, https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_480/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/escudo-alcaldia-480x430.png 480w" data-sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 512px, 100vw" class="lazyload wp-image-209607" /></span></div></div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_2_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_1_tb_footer"> <span class="et_pb_image_wrap "><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/WhatsApp-Image-2025-05-27-at-8.09.49 a.m.-1.png" alt="" title="" /></noscript><img class="lazyload" decoding="async" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20210%20140%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/WhatsApp-Image-2025-05-27-at-8.09.49 a.m.-1.png" alt="" title="" /></span></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_with_border et_pb_row et_pb_row_1_tb_footer et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters4"><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_3_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_1_tb_footer  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><ul class="px-0" style="list-style: none; padding: 0px;"><li><strong>Dirección Fase I:</strong> Calle 35 # 10-43, Bucaramanga, Santander, Colombia.</li><li><strong>Dirección Fase II:</strong> Carrera 11 # 34-52, Bucaramanga, Santander, Colombia</li><li><strong>Código Postal:</strong> 680006. Código Dane: 68001.</li><li><strong>Horario de Atención:</strong> Lunes a jueves de 7:00 a.m. a 12:00 m y de 1:00 p.m. a 5:30 p.m. / viernes jornada continua en el horario de 7:00 a.m. a 5:00 p.m., con 30 minutos de descanso al medio día.</li><li><span><strong>Horario de Atención CAME (Central):</strong></span><div class="x_elementToProof" data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)" data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">Lunes a jueves:    7:00 a.m. a 12:00 m y de 1:00 p.m. a 5:30 p.m.<br />Viernes:          7:00 a.m. a 5:00 p.m. en Jornada Continua con 30 minutos de descanso al medio día.</div></li><li><span><strong>Horario de Atención CAME (Norte):</strong></span></li><li><div class="x_elementToProof"><span data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)" data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">Dirección: </span><span data-ogsc="black">Carrera 12 #16N-84 del barrio Kennedy.</span></div><div class="x_elementToProof" data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)">Horario habitual de lunes a viernes en<b> jornada continua de 7:30 a.m.  a 3:00 p.m.  </b></div></li><li><strong>Teléfono Conmutador: </strong>  +57 (607) 633 70 00</li><li><strong>Líneagratuita:</strong> +57 (607) 652 55 55</li><li><strong>Correo Institucional:</strong><span> </span><a href="mailto:contactenos@bucaramanga.gov.co">contactenos@bucaramanga.gov.co</a></li><li><strong>Correo de notificaciones judiciales:</strong><span> </span><a href="mailto:notificaciones@bucaramanga.gov.co">notificaciones@bucaramanga.gov.co</a></li><li><strong>Canal de denuncia para presuntos actos de corrupción: </strong><a href="https://canaldenuncia.bucaramanga.gov.co/">https://canaldenuncia.bucaramanga.gov.co/</a></li><li><strong>Emergencia: </strong><a href="https://emergencia.bucaramanga.gov.co/">https://emergencia.bucaramanga.gov.co/</a><strong></strong></li><li><strong>Radique aquí su queja disciplinaria: </strong><a href="https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/gobierno-ciudadanos-1/secretarias/oficina-de-control-interno-disciplinario/">https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/gobierno-ciudadanos-1/secretarias/oficina-de-control-interno-disciplinario/</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_2_tb_footer et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters4"><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4 et_pb_column_4_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_0_tb_footer  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_blurb_content"><div class="et_pb_main_blurb_image"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/alcaldiadebucaramanga/" target="_blank"><span class="et_pb_image_wrap"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="22" height="22" src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_22,h_22/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/icon_face.png" alt="" class="et-waypoint et_pb_animation_top et_pb_animation_top_tablet et_pb_animation_top_phone wp-image-1080" /></noscript><img decoding="async" width="22" height="22" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%2022%2022%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_22,h_22/https://www.bucaramanga.gov.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/icon_face.png" alt="" class="lazyload et-waypoint et_pb_animation_top et_pb_animation_top_tablet et_pb_animation_top_phone wp-image-1080" /></span></a></div><div class="et_pb_blurb_container"><h4 class="et_pb_module_header"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/alcaldiadebucaramanga/" target="_blank">Alcaldía de Bucaramanga</a></h4></div></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4 et_pb_column_5_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_1_tb_footer  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_blurb_content"><div class="et_pb_main_blurb_image"><a href="https://twitter.com/AlcaldiaBGA" target="_blank"><span class="et_pb_image_wrap"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="22" height="22" src="https://sp-ao.sh